{"blocks":[{"key":"b1uk0","text":"Inoculate experimental culture from the sub-culture created in Day 2 with 1:100 dilution of media to sub-culture.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5ih8i","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"dc47b","text":"In 125 mL flask add 25 mL of media and 250 µL of sub-culture. Repeat for each strain and biological replicate into its own flask.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
